693.TextCN:
心得胜利：
不犯规的情况下，先打进所有的目标球后，再将黑8打进即为获胜
失败:
1.还未将所有目标球打进球袋之前，就提前打进黑8
2.在击打最后一球时，白球与黑8同时进袋
3.在同一局比赛中，连续犯规达到3次也将判负
693.TextEN:
Victory in Experience:
If there is no foul, score all the target balls first, and then score Black 8 to win
Failed:
1. Before hitting all the target balls into the goal bag, he scored the black 8 in advance
2. When hitting the last ball, both the white and black balls enter the bag at the same time
3. In the same game, if the number of consecutive fouls reaches 3, it will also result in a loss

694.TextCN:
如何确定目标球:未确定目标时，通过击入全色球或花色球确定目标球目标球信息:
球桌上剩余的目标球个数
回合倒计时:
倒计时结束前必须要出杆，否则被视为犯规
694.TextEN:
How to determine the target ball: When the target is not determined, determine the target ball information by hitting the full color ball or flower color ball:
The remaining number of target balls on the table
Round Countdown:
A shot must be taken before the countdown ends, otherwise it will be considered a foul
